    • copy

      public static <T> T copy(T object) throws CloneNotSupportedException
      Returns a copy of the specified object, which should be a clone if the object is cloneable otherwise a reference to the specified object is returned. If the object is null this method returns null.
      Type Parameters:
      T - the object type.
      Parameters:
      object - the object to copy (null permitted).
      Returns:
      A clone of the specified object, or null.
      Throws:
      CloneNotSupportedException - if the object cannot be cloned.
